data.description: Looking for a home with a possible assumable loan with the interest rates of the past? Per owner, this FHA loan may be assumable!  This 4 bed 2 bath property offers lots of extras!  2 separate living areas, potential RV parking area, 32 panels of leased solar, even an outdoor kitchen!  Close to schools and shopping for convenient day to day life!  Make your appointment to view and talk with your agent to see if assumable financing will work for you!
